## Summary
Successfully implemented cross-platform signal handling utilities for graceful shutdown on Windows, macOS, and Linux.

## Implementation Details

### Core Utilities (`src/observability/utils.ts`)
- `setupShutdownHandlers(callback)`: Registers SIGINT on all platforms, SIGTERM only on Unix
- `gracefulShutdown(childProcess, timeoutMs)`: Sends SIGTERM on Unix, SIGINT on Windows with SIGKILL fallback

